{"tid":104604,"cid":17,"subCid":0,"title":"[問題兒童]想問日本東北 - 睇動物/貓/熊/草泥馬之旅","createTime":"2017-02-02T08:22:21.000Z","updateTime":"2017-02-03T01:55:02.000Z","uid":3900,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"83a021494f379a921d641e3a580f2cb7c642947a","tid":104604,"uid":3900,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-02T08:22:21.000Z","msg":"第1日 東京-JL-&gt;青森 (12點左右到青森) 住青森淺虫溫泉<br />\n第2日 青森 (弘前公園/弘前城)  住青森<br />\n第3日 盛岡 (小岩井牧場) 住盛岡<br />\n第4日 秋田 (北秋田熊牧場/角館) 住秋田<br />\n第5日 仙台 (白石 狐狸村/船岡) 住白石或仙台<br />\n第6日 仙台 (石卷 貓島)  住仙台<br />\n第7日 那須 (那須那須動物王國/草泥馬牧場) 住那須<br />\n第8日 日光/鬼怒川 (揀緊地方浸溫泉)<br />\n第9日 返香港<br />\n<br />\n我諗緊將第1/2日combine埋做1日<br />\n跟住加多1日其他地方或者延長個個地方逗留時間<br />\n<br />\n有無提意?<br />\n<br />\nthanks"},{"pid":"a7677ca8e96df3c00ec31fa8054edc258bb3f7d2","tid":104604,"uid":3900,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-02T09:20:01.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f0986502512c42974b53b149f7468e3593117bae","tid":104604,"uid":2660,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-02T09:49:35.000Z","msg":"第一日ok<br />\n但6點左右要係返弘前走<br />\n不過其實弘前公園同弘前城行唔到咁耐<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dc77fa1ea9fecab071d6592a0ac0ae3059ee6e01","tid":104604,"uid":15692,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-02T09:58:14.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>第一日ok<br />\n但6點左右要係返弘前走<br />\n不過其實弘前公園同弘前城行唔到咁耐<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n冬天成個弘前人影都無隻<br />\n去貓島你打算撘邊班船？如果早果班前一晚就要住仙台先得"},{"pid":"259f4e54a70d6f97cc64fd734b95c07c1f68687c","tid":104604,"uid":16506,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-02T10:03:43.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>第一日ok<br />\n但6點左右要係返弘前走<br />\n不過其實弘前公園同弘前城行唔到咁耐<im